title: Photo of the Day: Chris Hemsworth’s Thor Workout Is Insanely Adorable
text: Chris Hemsworth is very new to Instagram, but he already knows what type of photos to pose to get thousands of likes and comments, and to make the Internet collectively a bit weak at the knees. Case in point: the picture below. The handsome actor, as famous for his role as Thor in the Marvel Cinematic Universe as he is for his impressive physique and almost impossible good looks, posted it the other day.
